snippet.title: Light Switch Simulator | OFFICIAL Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Light Switch Simulator on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3147600/Light_Switch_Simulator/

The makers of Progress Bar Simulator (the most realistic simulation of progress bars ever created) bringing you this new epic experience.

* Developed & Published by: SpielmannSpiel https://spielmannspiel.com/
* Art: Megumi M https://megumi-m.die-kreativberatung.de/
* Voice: Geruhn https://geruhn.com/
